description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Put your reaction skills to the test in this no-fuss retro version of gaming's most trendy feature: Quick Time Events. Do you have what it takes to be the world's next QTE Champ?
